      "blocks": {
        "45f687e9-9e5e-4b1f-afcf-495758844ce1": {
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/waterbottles.webp",
            "label": "Sustainability Begins With",
            "orientation": "right",
            "stars": 0,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>We design our products with meticulous attention to detail and use high-quality materials. Each item is created with a commitment to quality and is intended to be used repeatedly. When used as instructed and properly cared for, a Simple Modern product can last for years, reducing waste exponentially over time.</p>",
            "title": "Building Drinkware That Lasts"
          },
          "type": "testimonial"
        },
        "94a21386-6cbf-4a84-91e5-fff56e719fd1": {
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/sustain.webp",
            "label": "Sustainability Begins With",
            "orientation": "left",
            "stars": 0,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>We believe sustainability starts at the beginning. We work hand-in-hand with our partners to implement sustainable practices, including recycling unused or damaged materials and packaging components. Our product packaging is made with fully-recyclable materials, and we are continually looking for ways to minimize printing and reduce use of paper and single use plastics, while still keeping products properly protected for our customers.</p>",
            "title": "Manufacturing Materials"
          },
          "type": "testimonial"
        },
        "a7264cc6-deca-4d34-aae2-6e0b07b93b30": {
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/TheFarm.jpg",
            "label": "Sustainability Begins With",
            "orientation": "right",
            "stars": 0,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>In 2022, Simple Modern began domestic manufacturing in Oklahoma City with a focus on reusable plastic water bottles. To date, Simple Modern has invested more than $6 million in domestic manufacturing, and the goal is to domestically produce more than 1.5 million units in Oklahoma in 2023. Domestic manufacturing reduces complexities and unnecessary logistics that add costs to customers and pollution to the environment.</p>",
            "title": "Manufacturing Practices"
          },
          "type": "testimonial"
        },
        "eae1605a-ac8b-43f2-a8a5-f2fb5af73562": {
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": "",
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/crop2.jpg",
            "label": "Sustainability Begins With",
            "orientation": "left",
            "stars": 0,
            "testimonial_text": "<p>Our rigorous and ever-improving quality control practices help us produce our drinkware correctly the first time. By doing so, we reduce waste, see fewer defects, and make certain that customers receive high-quality product.</p>",
            "title": "Quality Control And Inspection"
          },
